Package jade.core.mobility

Interface AgentMobilitySlice

All Superinterfaces:
Serializable, Service.Slice
All Known Implementing Classes:
AgentMobilityProxy
public interface AgentMobilitySlice extends Service.Slice
The horizontal interface for the JADE kernel-level service managing the mobility-related agent life cycle: migration and clonation.
Author:
Giovanni Rimassa - FRAMeTech s.r.l.
